    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "TASK-3-Custom Aggregation and Complete Sales Report"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "6d4BK2PyX-vN"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def sales_range(x):\n",
        "    return x.max() - x.min()\n",
        "print(\"custom function calculating range by giving min, max, sum, mean as inputs\")\n",
        "print(df.groupby('region')['sales_amount'].agg(['sum', 'mean', 'min', 'max', sales_range]).reset_index())\n",
        "print(\"Dict wise multi level agrregration on diff columns\")\n",
        "print(df.groupby('region').agg({\n",
        "    'sales_amount': ['sum', 'mean'],\n",
        "    'customer_id': 'count'\n",
        "}).reset_index())\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "vmIqrUNKYAUp",
        "outputId": "7a4f4253-3d4e-43a9-99c0-366fd13fbbd1",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "execution_count": 16,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "custom function calculating range by giving min, max, sum, mean as inputs\n",
            "  region        sum         mean     min      max  sales_range\n",
            "0   East   95189.81  2213.716512  307.82  4758.46      4450.64\n",
            "1  North  135181.16  2413.949286  110.71  4788.56      4677.85\n",
            "2  South  158977.36  2789.076491  373.45  4983.33      4609.88\n",
            "3   West  109383.07  2485.978864  203.60  4903.53      4699.93\n",
            "Dict wise multi level agrregration on diff columns\n",
            "  region sales_amount              customer_id\n",
            "                  sum         mean       count\n",
            "0   East     95189.81  2213.716512          43\n",
            "1  North    135181.16  2413.949286          56\n",
            "2  South    158977.36  2789.076491          57\n",
            "3   West    109383.07  2485.978864          44\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        " Difference between multi-level column structure that results from the dictionary-based aggregation and single aggregations is that\n",
        "**In multilevel column structure - for diff columns different functions can be performed at once whereas for single aggregation, only one column can be performed multiple functions **like sum, mean, count, etc.."
      ],
